First, locate your desktop.

Then search for:

Internet Explorer,
Safari,
Fire Fox,
And
Google Chrome,

It is likely that you will not find all of these, but any one should do the trick.

Now, double click the icon(s) you find.

A window should open similar to the one your are reading this in.

Now, near the top of the window (browser) there should be a text box. Depending on your browser and home page, the text inside it may vary.

You now click on that text box, and with your keyboard (rectangular shape with buttons on it) type in:

http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf

After pressing enter (can be found near the right half of the keyboard) you should be taken to the “Moparscape” TOS. After reading and accepting at your own will, you will be taken to the forums.
